Time-At version 0.01
====================

Time::At is a small wrapper around the at(1) timespec parser, so it can be
used in Perl programs.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

None.

